SCHEMA: materials/event_type_registry.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.materials.event_type_registry
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define construction provenance event type entries.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record event_type
  required:
    - schema_version: semver
    - event_type_id: id
    - description: string
    - extensions: map

INVARIANTS:
- event_type_id is stable and unique within provenance event type registry.
